The point is you have to be the spirit.

00:38:04.000 --> 00:38:07.000
All these doings are to be the spirit.

00:38:07.000 --> 00:38:13.000
It's not talking, it's not your mental projections, all your new ideas coming up and going up.

00:38:13.000 --> 00:38:18.000
It's not that, it is you have to be the spirit.

00:38:18.000 --> 00:38:25.000
Face it out.

